p: Table 10 presents calculated digestibility of nutrients, energy, essential amino acids and fatty acids in microalgal ingredients. We detected significantly higher ADC values for crude protein and energy in the N. oculata whole cells (81% and 80%) than the N. oculata co-product (74% and 73%). We did not detect significant differences between N. oculata whole cells and N. oculata co-product for the ADC of lipid. We detected the lowest ADC value of ash in the N. oculata whole cells (24%), compared with the N. oculata co-product (54%).
